12 SECTION 2. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
13 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 24-163 of Title 70, unless there
14 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
15 A. Institutions of higher education and public schools shall
16 integrate the definition of antisemitism provided for in Section 1
17 of this act into their student, faculty, and employee codes of
18 conduct. Prohibited conduct as it specifically relates to
19 antisemitism shall include harassment and discrimination against
20 Jews in compliance with Title VI of the Civil Rights Act of 1964 and
21 antidiscrimination regulations provided by the United States
22 Department of Education and the United States Department of Justice.
23 B. Institutions of higher education and public schools shall
24 treat harassment of or discrimination against students or employees
SB942 HFLR Page 4
